{"id":330281,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/01/【微历史】：何祚庥论证三个代表/","date":"2014-01-28T23:44:12Z","modified":"2015-03-18T23:18:36Z","title":"【微历史】：何祚庥论证三个代表","content":"<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/01/weilishi8.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-330282\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/01/weilishi8.jpg\" alt=\"weilishi8\" width=\"606\" height=\"421\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/01/weilishi8.jpg 606w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/01/weilishi8-300x208.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 606px) 100vw, 606px\" /></a></p>\n<p>阿里公鸡：1953年北京市开始酝酿大规模拆除古建筑。为挽救四朝古都仅存的完整牌楼街不因政治因素毁于一旦，梁思成与当时的领导人发生了激烈冲突。此时，对建筑一窍不通的何祚庥跳出来，在《学习》上发表文章，将梁思成保护古建筑的思想归结为“资产阶级的唯心主义”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.botanwang.com/articles/201401/〖微历史〗邓榕刘亭亭参与对卞仲耘的行凶.html\">图片来自网络</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/cdtimes/index.html?u=chinese\">中国数字时代亚马逊镜像</a>（墙内可直接点击）</p>\n","author":296,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016],"tags":[18835,9813,9997,24532,27335]}